{"tid":521084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新律政司長大宅多處涉僭建　鄭若驊發聲明致歉","createTime":"2018-01-06T06:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T06:45:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2806b47563fbeb953c12daee12efd3cd51f2dd2f","tid":521084,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"新任律政司司長鄭若驊今日上任，即被踢爆現居的屯門大欖3層獨立屋懷疑僭建。<br />\n<br />\n除《蘋果》發現該獨立屋加建天台玻璃貯物室、改動地下外牆、花園挖建水池等外，有傳媒懷疑鄭僭建地庫，全屋至少四處涉違規。鄭若驊以律政司司長發出聲明，指昨收到屋宇署通知，要求進入有關物業進行調查，她已為此委託專業認可人士進行檢視，並為是否有懷疑僭建物問題立即向特首報告。<br />\n<br />\n鄭表示會全加配合屋宇署的調查，若證實有僭建物會盡快改正，並為事件致歉。"},{"pid":"14d35859c639e5b5c21c158a8f9489afd4fa8caf","tid":521084,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180106/57672717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57672717&d=sUHPyzpocB2%2BpF4k5qrO7QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b24a2e30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57672717&h=68c115c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180106/57672717</a>"},{"pid":"2f2ea44f3cf4b582969b3d30f55ae73ccf99f109","tid":521084,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"辭職啦"},{"pid":"9af0b16ff1ebe60ba2ec3a2cf8d4a98313e68cc7","tid":521084,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"好快就合法化,咁就唔存在問題"},{"pid":"61762d32ba1e1259acd5abbf426d7257d83add60","tid":521084,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bec045b247bb80e12cf6a4446fc25e020721b01","tid":521084,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"